data.description: Look no further than this beautiful all brick home in Cornelius. Upon entry you'll find a wonderful open floor plan. The kitchen is spacious with maple cabinets, a butlers pantry, and includes a bright and sunny breakfast area. The kitchen also opens into the family room with a white marble surround fireplace. The main floor also includes a formal dining room, formal living room, private office, accessible bathroom, and laundry room. Upstairs, you'll find a large primary bedroom with on-suite bathroom featuring a separate shower, jetted tub, and a large walk-in closet. This level also includes 3 additional bedrooms a second full bath and a large bonus room with kitchen stair access, perfect for movie nights! The back custom deck looks over a large fenced-in yard. There is a large side entrance 2 car garage. With gas lite streets Heron Harbor has a community boat ramp picnic area and is conveniently located near Lake Norman parks, restaurants, shops, and I-77.
